{
  "name": "Ingest Health - Ingest Loss Watchdog",
  "description": "Hourly per-device ingest-loss detector. Async LRQ in a POLL LOOP (all result-consuming actions INSIDE the loop). Loop: poll(GET) -> if stepsCompleted = totalSteps read/branch/break, else delay 5s and re-poll (cap 60). Anti-joins ingestHealthSourceStats (active_hours>=151) vs live activity, emails {{NOTIFY_EMAIL}}. Bind 'SentinelOne SDL' (Bearer) on both http_request actions before activating.",
